📑 Notes:
Make sure to sign up on the OpenWeather API website and get your own API Key 🔑 for the app to fetch real-time weather data 🌤️.

If you face any issues, feel free to open an issue or submit a pull request 📝.

📌 Future Enhancements:
Add a background image that changes according to the weather (sunny, rainy, cloudy, etc.) 🌞🌧️

Improve error handling for invalid city names and show a user-friendly error message 🚨.

Add a dark mode toggle for the app 🌙.

Enable search by zip code 🔢.

